        "purpose": "transcribing",
        "value": "○佐嘉藩"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "modern_jp_reading",
        "value": "佐嘉藩（さがはん）— 古い表記。現代は「佐賀」"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Saga domain (written 佐嘉, the kyūjitai form; modern Japanese uses 佐賀). The ○ begins the entry; everything to its LEFT (reading right-to-left) is Saga's. The small 永 二百四十九兩… figure to the RIGHT of the marker is the tail of the PRECEDING domain. Saga has NO vol1 entry — it appears only in vol2 (the gap documented in reference_saga_HI_gap)."
      },
      {
        "purpose": "identifying",
        "value": "○佐嘉藩"
      }
    ],
