        "value": "貮口合 平均 米 七拾貳萬四千七百三拾九石三斗壹升五合貳勺"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "modern_jp_reading",
        "value": "貮口合 平均（にこうごう へいきん）米 七十二万四千七百三十九石余 — 五ヶ年平均"
      },
      {
        "purpose": "english_translation",
        "value": "Two-mouth combined, 5-year average = 724,739.3152 koku — Saga's distinctive phrasing for what is essentially godaka: formal + new-field high, averaged over five years. EXACT MATCH with the Tōkei Shūshi figure (724,739). The 貮口合 phrasing reflects the domain's split-territory administration."
      },
      {
        "purpose": "extracted_value",
        "value": "724,739.3152 koku"
